text:
That's amazing!
It feels like something I've never worn before!

Yeah, that's right.
It's a bit different from usual.

Yes!
I've seen this in Justice V before!

Is that so?
I don't recall anyone wearing it in Justice V. Who wore it?

Everyone did!
We all wore outfits like this and fought together, looking cool!

They fought in those...!?
So, they didn't transform... That's incredible!
Well, they do seem easy to move in, right...?

Yes!
It's really easy to move in!
I feel like I could fight cool battles in it too!
